<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.4">
<l>īcaṉ vāṉavark keṉpaṉeṉ ṟālatu</l>
<l>tēca mōtiru vēṅkaṭat tāṉukku</l>
<l>nīca ṉēṉiṟai voṉṟumi lēṉeṉkaṇ</l>
<l>pācam vaitta parañcuṭar cōtikkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you say “he is called the lord of the celestials”, is that</l>
<l>the land of him from sacred Vēṅkaṭam?</l>
<l>I am a low person, I have not a single accomplishment</l>
<l>for the highest glowing light that has placed a snare on me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
